<br>
Is there a website available for information on raiding certain zones?  The websites I frequent are allakhazam.com and eqatlas.com.<br>
<br>
Some specific questions I need answered:<br>
<br>
1) How many people are needed to raid Naggy?<br>
2) What levels are needed?<br>
3) What high-level mobs can we expect to run into along the way?<br>
4) What is the lowest level you would recomend for someone attending the raid?  IE We have several mid-30s in our guild who would like to go, but I'm not sure if they should.<br>
<br>
I already know about some of the things needed to attack Nagafen, such as fire and magic resists.  But any other information would be very helpful.<br>
