<br>
Make sure to have your buffing plan down well beforehand. You don't want the first group's buffs fading as the last group is gettting their's <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
