<br>
As for mobs encountered on the way, just the fire giants are your only worry..They are on a 8 hour spawn so shouldnt have a worry about medding between them and still have plenty of time to med/buff for Naggy. Also remind anyone that has it to use their discipline resistant. I was never feared once and resisted most of Naggy's spells.<br>
<br>
If you wish to do this raid, please count me in and I also will volunteerto be MA..<br>
